ZH: 这片土地贫瘠得无法种植庄稼。
EN: The land here is so barren that crops cannot be grown.

ZH: 这个山谷因为缺乏水源变得贫瘠不堪。
EN: This valley has become extremely barren due to the lack of water sources.

ZH: 这块地被连绵山脉所包围，非常贫瘠。
EN: This piece of land is surrounded by continuous mountain ranges, making it very impoverished.

ZH: 这个地区的土壤贫瘠，无法长出茂密的森林。
EN: The soil in this area is so infertile that dense forests cannot grow.

ZH: 这个国家的北部地区气候干燥，土地贫瘠。
EN: The northern region of this country has a dry climate with barren land.

ZH: 贫瘠的土地无法养活太多的家庭。
EN: Barren land cannot support too many families.

ZH: 由于缺乏雨水，这个省份的大部分地区都变得贫瘠了。
EN: Due to the lack of rainfall, most parts of this province have become impoverished.

ZH: 这片贫瘠的土地需要大量的肥料才能种植庄稼。
EN: This barren land requires a large amount of fertilizer to grow crops.

ZH: 贫瘠的土壤让这里的居民生活非常困难。
EN: The impoverished soil makes it very difficult for the residents here to live.

ZH: 这片地区的居民因为贫瘠的土壤而过着贫困的生活。
EN: The residents of this region live in poverty due to the barren soil.

ZH: 这片土地由于长时间的过度放牧而变得贫瘠不堪。
EN: This land has become extremely barren due to prolonged overgrazing.

ZH: 这个岛屿因为长期受到干旱的侵袭，成为贫瘠之地。
EN: This island has become a barren land as a result of prolonged drought.

ZH: 沙漠里的土地因为缺水而变得贫瘠不毛。
EN: The land in the desert has become barren and unproductive due to lack of water.

ZH: 由于环境破坏，这个地区的土地变得贫瘠不堪。
EN: Due to environmental damage, the land in this region has become extremely barren.

ZH: 这个村庄的周边地区都是贫瘠的山地，无法耕种。
EN: The surrounding areas of this village are all barren mountains that cannot be cultivated.

ZH: 这个国家的贫困地区主要集中在贫瘠的高原上。
EN: The poverty-stricken areas of this country are mainly concentrated in the barren plateau.

ZH: 这片高山地区由于地质条件恶劣而变得贫瘠无比。
EN: This mountainous region has become extremely barren due to its harsh geological conditions.

ZH: 这个沙漠是世界上最贫瘠的地方之一，几乎没有生命存在。
EN: This desert is one of the most barren places in the world, with almost no signs of life.

ZH: 这个地方的贫瘠土壤难以满足任何农作物的生长需求。
EN: The barren soil in this area cannot meet the growth requirements of any crops.

ZH: 这片贫瘠的地区需要大力改善土壤质量才能实现农田复垦。
EN: This barren area requires significant improvement in soil quality to achieve farmland reclamation.
